flowchart TD
    title Chapter 4: Pattern Matching Flow
    
    MatchExpr[match expression] --> PatternCheck{Pattern Match?}
    
    PatternCheck -->|pattern 1: literal| LitMatch[Literal Match]
    PatternCheck -->|pattern 2: variable| VarMatch[Variable Binding]
    PatternCheck -->|pattern 3: struct| StructMatch[Struct Destructure]
    PatternCheck -->|pattern 4: enum| EnumMatch[Enum Variant]
    PatternCheck -->|pattern 5: tuple| TupleMatch[Tuple Destructure]
    PatternCheck -->|pattern 6: reference| RefMatch[Reference Match]
    PatternCheck -->|pattern 7: slice| SliceMatch[Slice Match]
    PatternCheck -->|_ wildcard| WildcardMatch[Wildcard _]
    
    LitMatch --> GuardCheck1{if guard?}
    VarMatch --> GuardCheck2{if guard?}
    StructMatch --> GuardCheck3{if guard?}
    EnumMatch --> GuardCheck4{if guard?}
    
    GuardCheck1 -->|true| Execute1[Execute arm 1]
    GuardCheck1 -->|false| NextPattern1[Next pattern]
    
    GuardCheck2 -->|true| Execute2[Execute arm 2]
    GuardCheck2 -->|false| NextPattern2[Next pattern]
    
    GuardCheck3 -->|true| Execute3[Execute arm 3]
    GuardCheck3 -->|false| NextPattern3[Next pattern]
    
    GuardCheck4 -->|true| Execute4[Execute arm 4]
    GuardCheck4 -->|false| NextPattern4[Next pattern]
    
    Execute1 --> ReturnValue[Return value]
    Execute2 --> ReturnValue
    Execute3 --> ReturnValue
    Execute4 --> ReturnValue
    WildcardMatch --> ReturnValue
    
    NextPattern1 --> PatternCheck
    NextPattern2 --> PatternCheck
    NextPattern3 --> PatternCheck
    NextPattern4 --> PatternCheck
    
    style MatchExpr fill:#a5d8ff
    style PatternCheck fill:#fef3c7
    style ReturnValue fill:#b2f2bb
    style WildcardMatch fill:#ffc9c9
